node.text:
On outings with indecisive babies who want to be carried, then walk on their own, then carried again, the versatile Criss-Cross Sling Backpack from @PetuniaPickleBottom has you covered! 🥰 

It even has a water-resistant interior, so it’s ideal for toting everything from bottles to bathing suits after impromptu trips through the sprinkler. 💛 Use the link in our bio to buy one for your next adventure!
